{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I wouldn't have to go to school because I was now eight years old and if I went to school, I'd be exposed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the reason why they made me a girl is because as a boy it didn't work too well and they don't look if a girl is circumcised.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was much safer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had really long hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I hadn't had a haircut for two and a half years, so-- so my hair grew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't fashionable in those days, but then who cared about the fashion?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I looked up-- they made me look like a girl, yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They made me look like a retard girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I looked different.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So everyone teased me in the village because the next day and so on, my mother was supposed to be a sister of one of the-- or relative of one of the villagers and I was her retarded child and my father had perished.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was an officer in the Polish Army, Royal Polish, and he perished.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And well, but we were with sympathizers of the partisans so we were OK and nobody knew except the people-- the family that we were with, the farm that I was a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So but they were in secretive because their-- their son was also [INAUDIBLE] my father and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that masquerading lasted for about three or four months, which wasn't all that bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kids used to-- used to tease me, but I developed a defensive mechanism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've been able to-- I had the ability to see something or other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I was obviously developing into-- into a survivor already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I just-- I-- I developed a very good way of speaking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I used to spit on the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
